
The directory tests/ contain a number of scripts used in VMs to measure
throughput with netperf and to test different features.

test_id_range			Creates vxlan device with different ids
test_tcp_sendfile		Run on vm1. On vm2 you need to run netserver
test_tcp_stream			Run on vm1. On vm2 you need to run netserver
test_tcp_stream_bridge		Run on vm1. On the host you need to run netserver
test_tcp_stream_direct		Run on vm1. On vm2 you need to run netserver
test_udp_stream			Run on vm1. On vm2 you need to run netserver
